## ğŸ§© Overview
**ZAI Core** is a modular Python-based AI framework built by **Muhammad Zaidan**.  
Version **v0.2.0** introduces **Persistent Memory**, allowing ZAI Core to remember what it learns â€” permanently.

> â€œNow your AI remembers â€” even after shutdown.â€

