## âš™ï¸ Features (v0.2.0)
- ğŸ§  **Persistent Brain** â€” Memory is saved in `zai_memory.json`  
- ğŸ’¾ **Auto Save System** â€” Every `learn()` updates memory instantly  
- ğŸ” **Recall Intelligence** â€” Retrieve old knowledge anytime  
- ğŸ§© **Forget & Wipe** â€” Erase single or all stored memories  
- ğŸ§  **CLI Mode** â€” Use ZAI Core directly from terminal  
